                </button>
            </div>
        </header>
        <main class="flex-grow pt-20">
            <section class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-32 text-center">
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white leading-tight mb-4">Crafting
                    Spaces, Inspiring Life.</h1>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">We specialize in
                    bespoke furniture and interior design for workshops, spas, and coffee shops, turning your vision
                    into a tangible, beautiful reality.</p>
                <a class="bg-primary text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity inline-flex items-center"
                    href="#work">
                    View Our Portfolio
                    <span class="material-icons ml-2">arrow_forward</span>
                </a>
            </section>
